## Data Flow: Pipeline Execution

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Your App
    participant Engine as DexEngine
    participant Runner as PipelineRunner
    participant Connector as Connector
    participant DuckDB as DuckDB
    participant Store as DexStore
    participant Catalog as DataCatalog

    App->>Engine: run_pipeline("clean_users")
    Engine->>Runner: run(name, progress_cb)
    Runner->>Connector: read(source_config)
    Connector-->>DuckDB: PyArrow Table / DataFrame
    Runner->>Runner: Execute DAG (transforms → quality)
    Runner->>Store: record_lineage(parent_id, op, layer, src→dst, counts)
    Runner->>Store: record_pipeline_run(success, rows_in, rows_out, duration)
    Runner->>Catalog: register_output_table(name, layer, format, path, rows)
    Runner-->>Engine: PipelineResult
    Engine-->>App: PipelineResult
```

