## AI Layer: Query → Answer

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    UserQuery["User Query"] --> Embed["Embed Query\n(sentence-transformers)"]
    UserQuery --> Lexical["Lexical Search\nBM25 / Elasticsearch"]
    Embed --> VectorSearch["Vector Search\nDuckDB VSS / Qdrant"]
    Lexical --> Hybrid["Hybrid Merge\nRRF / Weighted"]
    VectorSearch --> Hybrid
    Hybrid --> Rerank["Cross-Encoder Rerank\n(optional)"]
    Rerank --> Context["Top-K Context\n+ Citations"]
    Context --> Router["ModelRouter\nSelect LLM + Guardrails"]
    Router --> Privacy["PrivacyGuard\nPII Mask/Redact/Hash\nAudit Log"]
    Privacy --> LLM["LLM Provider\nOllama / OpenAI / Anthropic"]
    LLM --> Answer["Answer + Citations"]
    Answer --> Memory["Store in\nLong-term / Episodic Memory"]
```

