## ML Lifecycle

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Experiment: train_experiment()
    Experiment --> Tracked: Tracker.log()
    Tracked --> Registered: ModelRegistry.register()
    Registered --> Staging: promote("staging")
    Staging --> Production: promote("production")
    Production --> Serving: ServingEngine.deploy()
    Serving --> Monitored: DriftScheduler.check()
    Monitored --> Drifted: drift_detected
    Drifted --> Retrain: trigger_retrain()
    Retrain --> Experiment
    Production --> Archived: promote("archived")
```

