## Deployment Topology (Kubernetes via infradex)

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph K8s["Kubernetes Cluster"]
        subgraph NS["namespace: dataenginex"]
            StudioPod["dex-studio\nDeployment (2 replicas)\nPort 8000"]
            APIPod["Your API\nDeployment (HPA)\nPort 8000"]
            WorkerPod["Background Worker\nDeployment / CronJob\n(arq + Redis)"]
        end

        subgraph Shared["Shared Services"]
            Redis["Redis\n(arq broker)"]
            Postgres["PostgreSQL\n(lineage, audit - optional)"]
            Qdrant["Qdrant\n(vector store - optional)"]
            MinIO["MinIO / S3\n(lakehouse - optional)"]
        end
    end

    subgraph External["External"]
        Ollama["Ollama / vLLM\n(LLM inference)"]
        MLflow["MLflow\n(tracking - optional)"]
        ES["Elasticsearch\n(lexical search - optional)"]
    end

    StudioPod -->|imports| DexLib["dataenginex Library"]
    APIPod -->|imports| DexLib
    WorkerPod -->|imports| DexLib

    DexLib -.->|SQLite WAL| PVC["PersistentVolume\n.dex/store.duckdb"]
    DexLib -.->|Parquet/Delta| MinIO
    DexLib -.->|Lineage/Audit| Postgres
    DexLib -.->|Vectors| Qdrant
    DexLib -.->|LLM Calls| Ollama
    DexLib -.->|Tracking| MLflow
    DexLib -.->|Lexical| ES
    WorkerPod -.->|Queue| Redis
```

